  "texts": [
    "We first download the raw drug label data, parse the labels' text, and extract the ADE relevant sections.",
    "There are two main categories in which the ADEs are presented -free text and in tables.",
    "For the free text, we utilize the PubMedBERT model fine-tuned on the FDA drug labels.",
    "For the structured or tabulated ADE text, we extract exact matched strings from the tables.",
    "As the Japanese drug labels are not in English, we use the MedDRA-J (the Japanese MedDRA vocabulary) to extract terms from the tabulated data, and machine translate the free text using GPT-4 into English to run the OnSIDES model on."
  ],
